# State Management Rules

State must follow feature boundaries.

State must not be shared globally unless necessary.

---

# State Location

Feature state must be located inside:

features/<feature>/model

Example

features/login/model/useLogin.ts

---

# Global State

Global state should be minimal.

Global state should exist only for:

authentication
theme
global settings

---

# State Principles

State must be predictable.

State updates must be explicit.

Avoid implicit side effects.
